Be in Hamaü for Alha Week!
October 22-29
Over 40 special events!
Five Hawaiian Islands present special
programs for Aloha Week. You'll see the
spectacular Royal Water and Hula Pageants ...
breathtaking Floral and International
Parades-other fascinating wonders.
There's exciting fun every minute...
especially when you go by Flying Clipper
—there's no faster, more luxurious
way to Hawaii.
Vin Grenache Rose
Cover Design
by Lillian Sader.
One of America's leading
young artists, Miss Sader
combines a deft color touch
with a sensitive flair
for intricate design.
For Hawaii,
she has created
a unique tableau of
these famous Hawaiian attractions—
Diamond Head
Surfing and Canoeing at Waikiki
Native Fisherman
Statue of King Kamehameha
A Hula Dancer, Palm Trees
Pineapples
and Various Hawaiian Plants
Fruit Cocktail, Hawaiian
Broiled Squab Chicken Maitre d'Hotel
Potatoes Duchess
French Cut String Beans Au Beurre
Rye and Parker House Roll

Champagne Almaden Brut
Marble Ice Cream, Wafers or Assorted Cheese Tray
